snippet.title: Prerelease video v0.2: Furniture, Weapons - StaudSoft's Synthetic World
snippet.description:
Buy the game on Desura: http://www.desura.com/games/staudsofts-synthetic-world

Hey I added a lot of stuff. I have now a construction table, boxes, chest, lamps, torches and for the lazy a bed.

And of course I added weapons:
- a pistole
- a stick
- a sword
- a knife

Enjoy!
